<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV12">
<l>pērkiṉ ṟatumaṇi māmai piṟaṅkiyaḷ ḷaṟpayalai</l>
<l>yūrkiṉ ṟatukaṅku lūḻika ḷēyitel lāmiṉavē</l>
<l>yīrkiṉṟa cakkarat temperu māṉkaṇṇaṉ taṇṇantuḻāyc</l>
<l>cārkiṉṟa naṉṉeñci ṉārtantu pōṉa taṉivaḷamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Departs [my] sapphire darkness. All over mud pallor</l>
<l>creeps up. Night [lasts] aeons. All this is like that,</l>
<l>the sole abundance given  to those with good hearts who approach</l>
<l>the cool Tulsi of Kaṇṇaṉ, our great lord with the cutting discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
